{"tid":1546401,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"致老師們","createTime":"2019-09-06T09:20:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T09:43:46.000Z","uid":307200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3f1c3a52f5eb30b6dc86e51c7ffb826e579d6436","tid":1546401,"uid":307200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T09:20:52.000Z","msg":"我地明白老師應該保持中立態度<br />\n同學生討論唔應該持有自己意見<br />\n<br />\n但講真 你既支持 對學生黎講<br />\n係會有好大既動力<br />\n<br />\n呢緊我知仲會有幾間學校會搞人鏈 連儂等等<br />\n唔係叫你寫memo 去拖手<br />\n<br />\n只不過希望當日你地可以著黑衫<br />\n特然唔想搭 <span style=\"color: red;\">地</span>鐵番學 轉搭巴士<br />\n又唔小心搭遠左 要走番段路番學<br />\n又或者驚學生整污糟學校地方<br />\n特登走去好多紙既地方睇下佢地有冇整污糟到<br />\n<br />\n最後最後 著咩色衫係我地既自由<br />\n病左就記得帶口罩<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"cee9c8d6a0cbcb668aa39d853853af9cfe878807","tid":1546401,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T09:21:29.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"21c91cb8fc63dd41cbc3c4284f4652eae6b6d229","tid":1546401,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T09:21:48.000Z","msg":"7/9機場更新 求求大家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1545323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1545323</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fg5HKFh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFg5HKFh.jpg&h=b79850f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-ur